Class AbstractClient.ClientListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • starvationevasion.client.MegaMawile.net.AbstractClient.ClientListener

    Enclosing class:
    AbstractClient

    class AbstractClient.ClientListener
extends java.lang.Thread
    The ClientListener is used to respond to server messages received through the ObjectInputStream, as well as print useful information to the console.
